snippet.title: Monster Prom 3: Monster Roadtrip x Cult of the Lamb - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase
snippet.description: Embark on a road trip like no other in this co-op narrative survival adventure. Visit fun locations, meet wacky characters, and manage your resources wisely. And yes: you still can date some hot monsters. This update launches on October 26, 2023 on PC.
